Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.64,0:00:08.56,VIOLET_staff,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(350,100)}{\blur2}中翻:牧尔伯特少佐 自动翻译人偶毛线 中校:愛を知らない雪梨 日听:犬 日校:cz 时轴:艾德曼银制锅 后期:冰喵 压制:军区司令cz
Comment: 0,0:00:20.57,0:00:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,jp
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.31,0:00:05.34,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}説得の余地などない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.51,0:00:09.53,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}愚行を働いた輩に対して手お下したまでだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.95,0:00:14.86,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}善人の皮をかぶった悪魔め 闇の底へと沈め
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.99,0:00:22.65,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}手を下したお前も 私と同類
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.77,0:00:25.89,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咎人の業火に焼かれるがいい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.78,0:00:34.16,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私は この罪を背負って生きるしかない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.33,0:00:36.28,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}この先 一生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.09,0:00:47.62,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}昨日のお芝居 すっごくよかった
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.26,0:00:50.69,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレットも観に行けばよかったのに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.70,0:00:53.93,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「赤い悪魔」でしたら 今戯曲を読んでいます
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.88,0:00:56.19,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あ～ いいな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.42,0:01:00.14,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}オスカー·ウェブスターの代筆なんて うらやましすげる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.19,0:01:03.75,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}だって 真っ先に彼の新作が読めるってことでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.15,0:01:07.18,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}完成したら 久しぶりの新作になるわね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.68,0:01:13.77,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「私は この罪を背負って生きるしかない」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.57,0:01:16.23,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「この先 一生」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:50.41,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はいこれ 代筆依頼書ね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.07,0:02:52.25,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}こんなに？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.26,0:02:54.67,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}公開恋文以来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.78,0:02:57.25,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレットちゃんの指名も増えたしね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.51,0:03:00.11,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.17,0:03:04.41,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}例の少佐のこと あの子に話した
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.23,0:03:06.00,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いや
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:11.32,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最近のあの子 時々何か考え込んでるみたいだから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.19,0:03:38.02,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.71,0:03:41.00,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自動手記人形サービスです
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.81,0:03:42.89,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何だそれは
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:45.84,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お初にお目にかかります
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.05,0:03:50.46,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お客様がお望みなら どこでも駆けつけます
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.11,0:03:52.91,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自動手記人形サービス
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.64,0:03:55.52,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレット·エヴァーガーデンです
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.97,0:03:58.65,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そこには少女がいた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:00.88,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}もう一度会いたかった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.12,0:04:04.27,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}名前すら 悲しくてささやけない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:08.75,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あの子と 同じ髪の色の少女が
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.30,0:04:10.83,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}しかし 驚いた
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:13.59,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}まさか こんな子供が来るとはな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:18.96,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ご希望に添えませんでしたら 別のドールを手配させていただきます
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.38,0:04:21.43,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いや タイプさえ打てれば
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:25.03,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}俺は今 ちょっと体調が
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.63,0:04:28.00,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}申し訳ありませんが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.48,0:04:32.71,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}仕事中はお酒を控えていただくよう お願い申し上げます
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.74,0:04:36.43,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}俺は飲まないと書けない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:38.56,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}書くのは私てす
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:41.50,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}じやあ 執筆は明日からにしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.06,0:04:46.39,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}困ったお方ですね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.01,0:04:49.58,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}執筆は この部屋で
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:51.09,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ここか テラスだな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.55,0:04:54.90,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}書斎はあるが あそこは狭くて息苦しい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.54,0:04:56.70,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}でしたら 今日は…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.06,0:05:01.15,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}その手は
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.68,0:05:06.63,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}戦争で失いました ですが 作業には問題ありません
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.01,0:05:19.93,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}旦那様 執筆に差し支えない程度には片づけました
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.37,0:05:22.50,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}タイプライターは持参しておりますが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.11,0:05:24.76,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}用紙はありますてしょうか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:29.38,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ないな 港の商店に売ってるから 買ってきてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.07,0:05:34.32,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それと夕食も カルボナーラがいい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.59,0:05:38.41,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}旦那様 私は代筆屋であってメイドでは
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.80,0:05:43.27,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}困ったお方です
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.33,0:05:48.86,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聞いたメニューの材料はそろえたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.45,0:05:50.85,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}*ありがとうございます
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.23,0:05:54.83,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どうしたんだい  何か付いてるかね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.34,0:05:59.20,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いえ これを 一体どうやって調理すればよいのてしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.20,0:06:02.44,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}殻を割って 黄身だけ取り分けて
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.26,0:06:04.25,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}きみ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:14.86,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何やってるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.48,0:06:17.43,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}料理に挑戦しております
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.12,0:06:31.54,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}まあ 初めてにしては上出来じゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.74,0:06:33.93,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君は食べないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:36.24,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私は あとていただきます
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:37.29,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.26,0:06:58.88,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何をなさっているんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.18,0:07:03.09,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}棚にあった酒をどこにやった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:04.69,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}隠しました
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.23,0:07:07.27,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}執筆作業の妨げになりますし
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.98,0:07:12.67,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それに… 旦那様ご自身にとってもよくはありません
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.09,0:07:15.91,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お預かりしてよるしいですね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.73,0:07:21.50,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}次 オリーブのセリフ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.56,0:07:24.56,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「この火の谷を越えないと
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.46,0:07:27.91,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怪物を倒す剣が手に入らないわ」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.50,0:07:31.12,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ト書き 水の精霊が現れる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.19,0:07:33.31,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}精霊のセリフ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.79,0:07:35.65,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「私が この火を消してあげる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:38.83,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうすればこの谷を越えられるわ」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.78,0:07:42.42,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}越えられるのですね よがったです
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.60,0:07:45.45,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ト書き 燃えている火が消える
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.12,0:07:48.67,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どうやって消えるのですか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.08,0:07:52.32,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}舞台上で はためいてた赤い布を引っ込めると
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.04,0:07:54.69,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}消えたように見えるだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.33,0:07:57.53,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}なるほど 了解しました
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:00.81,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}なあ どう思う
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.39,0:08:02.24,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}面白いか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.27,0:08:05.45,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何というか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.02,0:08:07.09,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何というか？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.95,0:08:09.76,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本当の話ではないのに
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:12.43,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自分が体験しているようです
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.13,0:08:17.83,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自分が このオリーブという少女と同じように
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.19,0:08:20.28,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喜んだり 悲しんだり
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.82,0:08:22.54,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不安になったりするのは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.07,0:08:24.57,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どうしてなのでしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:33.34,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それは 君が主人公と オリーブと 同じ気持ちになってくれてるってことだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.12,0:08:36.08,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}オリーブに共感してくれてるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:41.55,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君が そう感じてくれて ホッとした
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.80,0:08:45.99,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}子供向けの芝居を書くのは初めてでね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.64,0:08:50.36,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}このあと オリーブは火の谷を越えて
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.68,0:08:54.23,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}無事に剣を手に入れ 怪物を倒すのですよね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.90,0:08:55.63,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.82,0:09:00.77,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}でも その代わりに精霊使いの力を失ってしまうんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:04.92,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そんな… ではどうやって故郷へ戻るのてすか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.49,0:09:07.28,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}船も壊れてしめいめしたし
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:11.17,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そこは まだ考えてない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.56,0:09:12.65,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}考えないと
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.07,0:09:15.24,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}考えなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.77,0:09:17.74,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}父親が待つ家に帰れません
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.45,0:09:22.88,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}考えましたか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.80,0:09:30.14,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いい天気だな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.54,0:09:33.29,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いや よすぎるか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.01,0:09:35.87,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}旦那様
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:40.70,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}これは
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.95,0:09:45.51,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ただの傘だよ どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.38,0:09:49.45,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}とてもキレイな傘だと思いまして
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.54,0:09:57.67,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少し休ませてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:14.18,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いつか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:16.72,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いつか きっと見せてあげるね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.78,0:10:19.70,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}やめろ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.71,0:10:24.69,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}やめてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.33,0:10:27.55,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}申し訳ございません 勝てに傘を…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:28.41,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}もういい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:31.35,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}もういい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.41,0:10:33.27,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}帰ってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.32,0:10:39.00,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それでは お芝居が完成しいせん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:41.90,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}オリーブの物語が完結しません
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.92,0:10:47.10,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}旦那様は 心に何か隠していらっしゃるのではないですか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.81,0:10:53.51,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私には それをくみ取る能力がなく
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.72,0:10:57.40,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本当に申し訳ございません
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.32,0:11:03.52,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}俺は もう何も書けない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.02,0:11:06.15,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}だが このままじゃダメだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.83,0:11:13.55,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そう思って あの子に… オリビアに聞かせてやった話を完成させようと思って
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.29,0:11:15.06,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}オリビア？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.92,0:11:16.62,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.93,0:11:19.07,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}娘だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:22.29,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妻が病気で亡くなって
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.54,0:11:28.69,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}夏の別荘だった この屋敷へ 俺は娘と越してきた
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.76,0:11:33.02,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}母親がいなくて寂しかったと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.44,0:11:37.37,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}けど… けど そんな様子はこれっぽっちも見せず
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.73,0:11:41.88,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}むしろ 俺が仕事を頑張れるようにと
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.34,0:11:44.96,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いつも いろいろと手伝ってくれてたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.12,0:11:48.26,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そんな娘の好きなものが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.50,0:11:52.53,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}フリルの付いた日傘と 水鳥で…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.56,0:11:57.73,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いいな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.38,0:12:00.97,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私も この湖を渡って見たい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.56,0:12:04.06,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あの落ち葉の上なら歩けるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.01,0:12:09.78,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}傘を差して風を利用すれば できるかもしれないね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.65,0:12:15.85,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}オリビア
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.94,0:12:18.18,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.02,0:12:22.15,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私が湖を歩くところ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.42,0:12:25.61,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いつか きっと見せてあげるね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.17,0:12:27.32,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お父さん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.91,0:12:31.94,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そして
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.88,0:12:37.44,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}医者との不毛な押し問答を繰り返し
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.03,0:12:39.89,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}残された時間を過ごすため
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.43,0:12:42.84,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}俺は娘を連れて戻ることにした
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.48,0:12:47.00,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}久しぶりの娘の笑顔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.21,0:12:50.26,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}穏やかで優しい日々
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.21,0:12:52.02,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}だが
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.99,0:12:55.48,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}たった1つの希望が…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.86,0:13:00.11,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}神は どれだけ俺の大切なものを
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:05.59,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大切な人と別れるということは
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.37,0:13:09.54,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}二度と会えないということは
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:12.28,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}こんなにも寂しく
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:17.93,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}こんなにも つらいことなのですね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:33.87,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}さっきは すまなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.67,0:13:37.44,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いえ おつらいのは旦那様ですのに
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.60,0:13:41.02,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私のほうが取り乱してしまい 申し訳ありません
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.67,0:13:45.90,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}完成させるよ オリーブの物語を
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.74,0:13:50.15,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少女は帰ってきて 父親と再会する
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:52.58,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どんなにつらい冒険をしたとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.08,0:13:54.80,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最後ハッピーエンドだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:13:58.65,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}主人公も観客も幸せになる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.80,0:14:00.92,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いや してみせる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.73,0:14:06.54,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そして 倒れる怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.98,0:14:07.87,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}オリーブ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.34,0:14:10.43,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「ついに怪物を倒したわ」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:11.99,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}水の精霊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.46,0:14:13.71,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「よくやったわ」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.98,0:14:15.44,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}風の精霊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.47,0:14:19.61,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「私たちは戻るなければ 精霊の世界に」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:21.43,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}火の精霊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.60,0:14:22.91,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「ここで お別れよ」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.60,0:14:24.93,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}立ち尽くす オリーブ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.44,0:14:30.50,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}さて ここから どうやってオリーブを家に帰すか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:34.32,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}船は壊れてしまったので 飛行機ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.58,0:14:38.73,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}もっと夢があるような方法で
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.01,0:14:42.68,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鳥でしたら 飛んで帰れますが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.55,0:14:45.90,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}傘で飛ぶのは どうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.26,0:14:47.48,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}傘では飛べません
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.77,0:14:50.84,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}飛べるんだ 風の精霊がもう一度だけ現れて言う
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.06,0:14:54.85,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「オリーブ あなたの傘を広げて」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.06,0:14:58.84,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君 傘を広げてみてくれないか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.48,0:15:03.41,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「その傘が あなたの翼よ」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.43,0:15:05.67,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「高く飛ぶと 風に流されるから」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.15,0:15:07.33,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「海では波を
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.58,0:15:08.57,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}川では岩を
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:11.52,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}湖では 落ち葉を踏んで行きなさい」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.74,0:15:14.11,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ステキな着想です
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.30,0:15:18.36,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}だろ？ 戻ってきたオリーブは 父親に再会する
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.02,0:15:22.17,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そして 海を渡って帰ってきて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.56,0:15:25.67,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再会して ひと言目 何を言うかな…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.12,0:15:27.08,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「ただいま」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.49,0:15:29.51,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いや 「お父さん」？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.10,0:15:31.57,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}また行き詰まったのですか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.77,0:15:36.68,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君 ちょっと向こうから歩いてきてくれないか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.13,0:15:38.67,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}イメージをつかみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:40.50,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}歩くだけでいいのですか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.41,0:15:44.27,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}できたら 湖に浮かぶ木の葉の上をね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.89,0:15:46.00,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}了解しました
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.12,0:15:51.23,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いや 今のは…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.23,0:16:15.52,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いいな 私も この湖を渡ってみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.91,0:16:20.20,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あの落ち葉の上なら 歩けるかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:24.01,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いつか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:26.83,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いつか きっと見せてあげるね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.62,0:16:28.79,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お父さん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.69,0:16:38.09,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あと何千回だって そう呼ばれたかった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.54,0:16:42.90,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}死なないでほしかったな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.17,0:16:57.21,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生きて… 大きく育って… ほしかったな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.08,0:17:19.61,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ご覧になられましたか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.59,0:17:24.49,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}３歩は歩いていたと思います
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.43,0:17:28.42,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}旦那様？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.73,0:17:33.72,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どうなされました お体の具合でも悪いのでしょうか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.48,0:17:38.42,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奇跡をかなえてくれた彼女に 俺は言った
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.15,0:17:41.25,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「神様なんていないと思っていたけど」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.84,0:17:43.83,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「いるなら 君のことだろう」と
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.11,0:17:51.87,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本当に この傘を頂いてよろしいのでしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.21,0:17:53.18,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.94,0:17:56.03,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}もっと飛べると思っていたのですが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.72,0:17:57.60,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}十分だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.82,0:18:02.73,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君は死んだ娘の「いつか きっと」をかなえてくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:07.19,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「いつか きっと」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.33,0:18:11.20,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それでは
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:17.69,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自動手記人形サーブすのご利用 誠にありがとうございました
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.47,0:18:20.15,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}こちらこそ ありがどう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:23.84,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴぁリオレット·エヴァーガーデン
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.99,0:18:36.78,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多くの命を奪った その手で
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.94,0:18:39.63,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人を結ぶ手紙を書くのか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.90,0:18:44.81,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君は自分がしてきたことで どんどん体に火がついて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.88,0:18:47.48,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}燃え上がっていることをまだ知らない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.57,0:18:49.66,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私は…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.66,0:18:50.77,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}燃えてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.53,0:18:54.79,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いつか 俺が言ったことが分かる時が来る
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.96,0:18:59.04,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そして初めて 自分が たくさんヤケドしていることに気づくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:08.52,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.02,0:19:09.89,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生きて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.56,0:19:11.81,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いいのですか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.83,0:19:14.47,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自由になりなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.37,0:19:17.60,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}武器として人をあやめてきた私が
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.14,0:19:19.61,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それでいいのですか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:26.41,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私は誰かの「いつか きっと」を奪ったのではないのですか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.42,0:19:32.67,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そして その人たちにも 愛する相手がいたのではないですか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.29,0:19:34.38,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}燃えていません
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:35.90,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}燃えています
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:37.44,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}燃えていません
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.68,0:19:39.22,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}燃えています
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:42.93,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自分がしてきたことでどんどん体に火がついて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.28,0:19:44.63,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}燃え上がっています
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.56,0:20:03.48,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あら
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.51,0:20:06.84,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あなた ヴァイオレット
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.42,0:20:11.62,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奥様 いつぞやは 大変失礼をいたしました
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.57,0:20:17.49,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奥様のお心を傷つけてしまい 誠に申し訳ございませんでした
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.84,0:20:21.20,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレット そんな いいのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.22,0:20:22.96,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}顔を上げてちょうだい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.07,0:20:29.20,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}よかった あなたが立派になって
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.54,0:20:32.83,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}浮かばれるわね 亡くなったギルべルトも
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:38.41,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}亡くなった？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.81,0:20:43.11,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生きているとおっしゃいましたよね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.71,0:20:45.67,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐は ご無事なのですよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:48.10,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それは…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.59,0:20:51.24,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生きていらっしやるのですよね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.50,0:20:56.67,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}すまない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.65,0:21:00.43,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どうしても 君に言えなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.13,0:21:04.26,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}インテンス最終決戦のあと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.98,0:21:08.03,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聖堂の下で 君は1人倒れていた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.01,0:21:13.38,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}恐らく砲撃を食らう寸前 あいつは君を突き飛ばしたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.43,0:21:19.70,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あいつは確認できなかったが がレキの下に認識票があった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.59,0:21:22.91,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それで 未帰還扱いになって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.37,0:21:24.64,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}では 分かれません
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.18,0:21:27.09,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}だが あの状況では
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.42,0:21:29.12,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐は きっとご無事です
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.81,0:21:30.84,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレットちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.88,0:21:31.92,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ご無事です
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.98,0:21:36.40,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレットちゃん 分かってくれ あいつはもう…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.41,0:21:39.03,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}分かりません 分かれません
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.30,0:21:42.75,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どうして どうして私だけ おかしいです
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.25,0:21:47.65,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そばには少佐がいらしていたのに そして 私に…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.58,0:21:51.88,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレットちゃん つらくても受け入れるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.30,0:21:54.45,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレットちゃん！
Comment: 0,0:00:21.14,0:00:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,ch
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.31,0:00:05.34,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你的话毫无说服力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.51,0:00:09.53,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}做了蠢事的家伙就该接受制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.95,0:00:14.86,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你这个伪装成善人的恶魔 堕入黑暗的深渊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.99,0:00:22.65,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}亲手执行制裁的你 和我也是一丘之貉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.77,0:00:25.89,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}承受罪人业火的灼烧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.78,0:00:34.16,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我只能背负着这份罪恶活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.33,0:00:36.28,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}今后一生亦是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.09,0:00:47.62,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}昨天的戏剧真是太精彩了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.26,0:00:50.69,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}早知道让薇尔莉特也一起去看了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.70,0:00:53.93,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}如果是说《红恶魔》 我正在看剧本
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.88,0:00:56.19,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.42,0:01:00.14,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}真羡慕你能为奥斯卡·韦伯斯特代笔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.19,0:01:03.75,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}因为这样就能最先看到他的新作品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.15,0:01:07.18,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}如果写完 这就是他久违的新作品呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.68,0:01:13.77,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}「我只能背负着这份罪恶活下去」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.57,0:01:16.23,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}「今后一生亦是」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:50.41,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}给 这是代笔委托书
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.07,0:02:52.25,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这么多？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.26,0:02:54.67,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}公开情书一事以来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.78,0:02:57.25,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}指名薇尔莉特的工作也增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.51,0:03:00.11,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}话说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.17,0:03:04.41,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那位少佐的事情 你跟她说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.23,0:03:06.00,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:11.32,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}最近那孩子时不时会陷入沉思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.19,0:03:38.02,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.71,0:03:41.00,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这里是自动手记人偶服务
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.81,0:03:42.89,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:45.84,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.05,0:03:50.46,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}只要客人有要求 不论身在何处 都能为您服务
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.11,0:03:52.91,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我是自动手记人偶服务
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.64,0:03:55.52,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特·伊芙加登
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.97,0:03:58.65,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那里站着一位少女
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:00.88,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我渴望再次见到的她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.12,0:04:04.27,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那让我悲痛到连她名字也念不出的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:08.75,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这位少女和她有着同样的发色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.30,0:04:10.83,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}着实吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:13.59,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没想到会派这么个小孩过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:18.96,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}如果您不满意 我们可以安排别的人偶前来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.38,0:04:21.43,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不用 能打字就行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:25.03,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我现在身体不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.63,0:04:28.00,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}虽然非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.48,0:04:32.71,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但我希望您在工作期间能控制酒量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.74,0:04:36.43,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我不喝酒就写不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:38.56,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我来负责写字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:41.50,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那明天再开始写作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.06,0:04:46.39,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}真让人为难
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.01,0:04:49.58,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}就在这个房间里写吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:51.09,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}在这里或者去露台
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.55,0:04:54.90,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}虽然有书房 但那里又窄又闷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.54,0:04:56.70,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那么今天…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.06,0:05:01.15,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你的手怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.68,0:05:06.63,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我在战争中失去了手 不过不妨碍工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.01,0:05:19.93,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}老爷 已经整理到不会妨碍写作的程度了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.37,0:05:22.50,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我带了打字机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.11,0:05:24.76,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}请问有打字机用纸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:29.38,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没有啊 港口的商店有卖 去买点回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.07,0:05:34.32,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}还有晚饭 我想吃培根蛋酱意面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.59,0:05:38.41,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}老爷 我是代笔员不是女仆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.80,0:05:43.27,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}真让人为难
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.33,0:05:48.86,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你说的菜 食材都在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.45,0:05:50.85,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.23,0:05:54.83,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}怎么了 上面粘有什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.34,0:05:59.20,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不 我在想应该如何烹饪这个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.20,0:06:02.44,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}把蛋壳敲开 只取蛋黄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.26,0:06:04.25,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}蛋黄？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:14.86,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.48,0:06:17.43,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我在尝试做饭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.12,0:06:31.54,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯 第一次做饭还算不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.74,0:06:33.93,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你不吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:36.24,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我待会再吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:37.29,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.26,0:06:58.88,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}您在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.18,0:07:03.09,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}柜子里的酒都到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:04.69,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我藏起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.23,0:07:07.27,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}酒不仅会影响写作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.98,0:07:12.67,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}还对老爷您的身体不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.09,0:07:15.91,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}就交给我保管吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.73,0:07:21.50,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}接下来 奥利弗的台词
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.56,0:07:24.56,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}「我必须通过这火焰谷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.46,0:07:27.91,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}才能获得能打倒怪物的宝剑」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.50,0:07:31.12,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}注 水精灵登场
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.19,0:07:33.31,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}精灵的台词
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.79,0:07:35.65,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}「我来帮你浇灭火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:38.83,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这样你就能穿过这座山谷」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.78,0:07:42.42,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}能穿过去了 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.60,0:07:45.45,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}注 燃烧着的火焰熄灭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.12,0:07:48.67,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}要怎样熄灭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.08,0:07:52.32,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}把舞台上的红旗子收起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.04,0:07:54.69,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}看上去就像火焰熄灭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.33,0:07:57.53,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}原来如此 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:00.81,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我说 你怎么看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.39,0:08:02.24,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}有趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.27,0:08:05.45,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.02,0:08:07.09,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}怎么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.95,0:08:09.76,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}明明知道这不是真实的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:12.43,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}却仿佛身临其境
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.13,0:08:17.83,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}自己就像这位名为奥利弗的少女一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.19,0:08:20.28,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}时而开心 时而悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.82,0:08:22.54,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}还会感到不安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.07,0:08:24.57,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这是为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:33.34,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}因为你和主人公奥利弗有了同样的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.12,0:08:36.08,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}和奥利弗产生了共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:41.55,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你能有这种感觉 我就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.80,0:08:45.99,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我还是第一次写面向孩子的戏剧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.64,0:08:50.36,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}在这之后奥利弗将穿过火焰谷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.68,0:08:54.23,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}顺利得到宝剑 然后打倒怪物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.90,0:08:55.63,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.82,0:09:00.77,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但作为代价她将失去精灵使的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:04.92,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}怎么会…那她要如何回到故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.49,0:09:07.28,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}船也坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:11.17,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那里我还没想好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.56,0:09:12.65,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}要想出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.07,0:09:15.24,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}想不出来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.77,0:09:17.74,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}她就回不去有父亲在等待着的家了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.45,0:09:22.88,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}您想过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.80,0:09:30.14,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}天气真好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.54,0:09:33.29,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不 是好过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.01,0:09:35.87,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}老爷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:40.70,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.95,0:09:45.51,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}一把伞而已 为什么问这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.38,0:09:49.45,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我觉得这把伞非常漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.54,0:09:57.67,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}让我稍微休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:14.18,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}以后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:16.72,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}以后一定让你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.78,0:10:19.70,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.71,0:10:24.69,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.33,0:10:27.55,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}非常抱歉 我不该擅自把伞…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:28.41,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}够了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:31.35,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.41,0:10:33.27,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.32,0:10:39.00,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这样戏剧就没法完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:41.90,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}奥利弗的故事就没法完结了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.92,0:10:47.10,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}老爷是不是有什么心事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.81,0:10:53.51,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我无法提炼出您的心事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.72,0:10:57.40,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}实在非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.32,0:11:03.52,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我已经写不出任何东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.02,0:11:06.15,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但我觉得这样下去不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.83,0:11:13.55,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}所以才想写完原本打算说给奥利维亚听的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.29,0:11:15.06,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}奥利维亚？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.92,0:11:16.62,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.93,0:11:19.07,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是我的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:22.29,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}妻子病逝之后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.54,0:11:28.69,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我和女儿搬到了这间 以前夏天住的别墅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.76,0:11:33.02,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我觉得她失去了母亲会很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.44,0:11:37.37,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}可是她一点都没有表现出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.73,0:11:41.88,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}倒不如说 为了让我努力工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.34,0:11:44.96,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}平时一直帮我做很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.12,0:11:48.26,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我这么一个女儿 她喜欢的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.50,0:11:52.53,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是带褶边的遮阳伞 和水鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.56,0:11:57.73,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.38,0:12:00.97,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我也想渡过这片湖水
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.56,0:12:04.06,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那些落叶上是不是能走路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.01,0:12:09.78,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}撑开伞利用风的力量 说不定可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.65,0:12:15.85,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}奥利维亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.94,0:12:18.18,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.02,0:12:22.15,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我在湖面上行走的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.42,0:12:25.61,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}以后一定让你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.17,0:12:27.32,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.91,0:12:31.94,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}后来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.88,0:12:37.44,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我和医生一遍遍重复无用的争论
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.03,0:12:39.89,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}为了和她一起度过余下的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.43,0:12:42.84,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我把女儿带回了家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.48,0:12:47.00,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}女儿久违的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.21,0:12:50.26,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}安稳的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.21,0:12:52.02,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}然而
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.99,0:12:55.48,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我唯一的希望…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.86,0:13:00.11,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}神究竟想夺走多少我珍惜的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:05.59,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}和珍惜的人分别
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.37,0:13:09.54,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}再也见不到她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:12.28,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}原来是这么令人寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:17.93,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是这么难受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:33.87,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}早上的事抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.67,0:13:37.44,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没事 明明难过的人是老爷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.60,0:13:41.02,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}而我却失态了 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.67,0:13:45.90,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我会把奥利弗的故事写完的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.74,0:13:50.15,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}少女会回到家乡 与父亲重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:52.58,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}无论经历多少痛苦的冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.08,0:13:54.80,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}最后都要迎来幸福结局
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:13:58.65,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}主人公和观众们都会幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.80,0:14:00.92,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不 我要让他们幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.73,0:14:06.54,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}然后怪物被打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.98,0:14:07.87,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}奥利弗说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.34,0:14:10.43,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}「终于打倒怪物了」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:11.99,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}水精灵说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.46,0:14:13.71,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}「干的真棒」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.98,0:14:15.44,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}风精灵说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.47,0:14:19.61,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}「我们必须回精灵世界去了」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:21.43,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}火精灵说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.60,0:14:22.91,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}「就在这道别吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.60,0:14:24.93,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}留到最后的奥利弗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.44,0:14:30.50,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好了 接下来要如何让奥利弗回家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:34.32,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}船已经坏了 要坐飞机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.58,0:14:38.73,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}方法要更梦幻一点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.01,0:14:42.68,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}如果是鸟 就能飞回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.55,0:14:45.90,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}用伞飞回去如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.26,0:14:47.48,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}用伞飞不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.77,0:14:50.84,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}能飞起来 风精灵再次出现说道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.06,0:14:54.85,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}「奥利弗 撑开你的伞」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.06,0:14:58.84,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你能撑开伞让我看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.48,0:15:03.41,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}「这把伞就是你的翅膀」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.43,0:15:05.67,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}高高跃起就能乘风而行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.15,0:15:07.33,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}踏着海上的波浪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.58,0:15:08.57,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}河里的岩石
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:11.52,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}湖中的落叶走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.74,0:15:14.11,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这个构思非常棒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.30,0:15:18.36,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}对吧 回到家乡的奥利弗和父亲重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.02,0:15:22.17,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}然后 漂洋过海回到家里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.56,0:15:25.67,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}重逢后的第一句话该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.12,0:15:27.08,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}「我回来了」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.49,0:15:29.51,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不 还是「爸爸」？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.10,0:15:31.57,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}又陷入瓶颈了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.77,0:15:36.68,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你能从那边走过来看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.13,0:15:38.67,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我想找一下感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:40.50,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}走过来就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.41,0:15:44.27,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}可以的话踩着湖面上的树叶过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.89,0:15:46.00,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.12,0:15:51.23,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}等等 刚刚说的只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.23,0:16:15.52,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}真好啊 我也想渡过这片湖水
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.91,0:16:20.20,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那些落叶上是不是能走路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:24.01,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}以后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:26.83,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}以后一定让你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.62,0:16:28.79,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.69,0:16:38.09,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我还想让你这样 叫我上千次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.54,0:16:42.90,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我好希望 你别死去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.17,0:16:57.21,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}真希望你活着 把你养大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.08,0:17:19.61,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}您看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.59,0:17:24.49,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}应该走了三步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.43,0:17:28.42,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}老爷？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.73,0:17:33.72,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}您怎么了 身体不舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.48,0:17:38.42,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}她实现了奇迹 我对她说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.15,0:17:41.25,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我本以为不存在什么神明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.84,0:17:43.83,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}如果存在 指的就是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.11,0:17:51.87,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我真的能收下这把伞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.21,0:17:53.18,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.94,0:17:56.03,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}本以为能飞得更远
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.72,0:17:57.60,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}足够远了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.82,0:18:02.73,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你实现了 我死去女儿的「以后一定」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:07.19,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}「以后一定」…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.33,0:18:11.20,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:17.69,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}非常感谢您使用自动手记人偶服务
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.47,0:18:20.15,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我才要感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:23.84,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特·伊芙加登
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.99,0:18:36.78,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}用你那夺走了众多性命的双手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.94,0:18:39.63,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}去写为人们结缘的书信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.90,0:18:44.81,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你因为自己做过的事 不断地引火烧身
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.88,0:18:47.48,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你还不知道自己在燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.57,0:18:49.66,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.66,0:18:50.77,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}烧起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.53,0:18:54.79,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}总有一天 你会明白我所说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.96,0:18:59.04,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}然后才意识到自己早已烧到遍体鳞伤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:08.52,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.02,0:19:09.89,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.56,0:19:11.81,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.83,0:19:14.47,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}自由地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.37,0:19:17.60,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}作为武器杀害他人的我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.14,0:19:19.61,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这样真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:26.41,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我是不是也夺走了别人的「以后一定」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.42,0:19:32.67,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}而那些人 是不是也有心爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.29,0:19:34.38,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没有烧起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:35.90,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}烧起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:37.44,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没有烧起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.68,0:19:39.22,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}烧起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:42.93,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}因为自己做过的事 不断地引火烧身
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.28,0:19:44.63,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}已经在燃烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.56,0:20:03.48,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.51,0:20:06.84,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是你 薇尔莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.42,0:20:11.62,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}夫人 以前真是太失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.57,0:20:17.49,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}伤了夫人的心 实在非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.84,0:20:21.20,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特 不用这样 没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.22,0:20:22.96,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}抬起头来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.07,0:20:29.20,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}太好了 你现在这么出息了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.54,0:20:32.83,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}逝去的基尔伯特也能瞑目了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:38.41,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}逝去的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.81,0:20:43.11,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你说过他还活着的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.71,0:20:45.67,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}少佐他还平安的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:48.10,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.59,0:20:51.24,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}他还活着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.50,0:20:56.67,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.65,0:21:00.43,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我怎么也说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.13,0:21:04.26,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}因坦斯最后决战之后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.98,0:21:08.03,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你一个人倒在圣堂下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.01,0:21:13.38,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}可能是在炮弹击中之前 他把你撞开了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.43,0:21:19.70,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}虽然没能找到他 但在瓦砾下有他的识别牌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.59,0:21:22.91,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}然后就作阵亡处理
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.37,0:21:24.64,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但我无法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.18,0:21:27.09,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但在那种情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.42,0:21:29.12,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}少佐一定还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.81,0:21:30.84,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.88,0:21:31.92,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.98,0:21:36.40,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特 希望你理解 他已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.41,0:21:39.03,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我不理解 我不理解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.30,0:21:42.75,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}为什么 为什么只有我活下来了 这很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.25,0:21:47.65,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}少佐明明就在我身边 还对我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.58,0:21:51.88,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特 就算很痛苦也要接受事实
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.30,0:21:54.45,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特！
