Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.43,0:01:24.03,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}知らない言葉を　覚えてゆくたび
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.13,0:01:30.53,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}おもかげのなか　手を伸ばすの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.80,0:01:37.13,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}だけど一人では　分からない言葉も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.55,0:01:40.64,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}あるのかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.95,0:01:45.23,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}さよならは　苦くて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.64,0:01:52.29,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}アイシテルは　遠いにおいがした
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.04,0:02:00.38,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}例えようのない　この思いは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.66,0:02:07.70,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}とても怖くて　だけど　とても愛おしくて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.74,0:02:13.96,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}わたし　なんで　泣いてるんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.00,0:02:20.69,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}心になんて　答えたらいい？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.83,0:02:27.44,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}言葉はいつでも　語るでもなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.49,0:02:33.68,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}そこにあるばかり　つのるばかり
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.85,0:02:42.52,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}わたしは　あなたに　会いたくなる
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.43,0:01:24.03,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}每当记忆陌生词汇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.13,0:01:30.53,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}双手便不由自主   伸向旧日光景
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.80,0:01:37.13,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}但孤身一人    也许有些话语
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.55,0:01:40.64,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}难以领悟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.95,0:01:45.23,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}一句「再见」伤感不已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.64,0:01:52.29,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}一声「爱你」遥不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.04,0:02:00.38,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}这份思念无法言喻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.66,0:02:07.70,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}让人惶恐    却又无比令人怜惜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.74,0:02:13.96,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}我眼中的泪 到底为何而流
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.00,0:02:20.69,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}纠缠不清的心 到底如何回应
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.83,0:02:27.44,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}总会口不对心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.49,0:02:33.68,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}埋藏在心里    一句又一句
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.85,0:02:42.52,VIOLET_opch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}我止不住地想见到你
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,——ED——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.50,0:22:21.26,VIOLET_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}あなたの声がみちしるべ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.59,0:22:42.72,VIOLET_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}一羽の鳥が　鳴いている
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.37,0:22:53.78,VIOLET_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}名前のない空に　わたしを探して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.19,0:22:59.60,VIOLET_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}優しさで編み続けた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.86,0:23:05.24,VIOLET_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}ゆりかごで明日へ行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.38,0:23:11.27,VIOLET_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}晴れの日も雨の日にも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.59,0:23:15.96,VIOLET_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}あなたを守るために
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.44,0:23:26.87,VIOLET_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}かけがえのない宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.45,0:23:37.69,VIOLET_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}名前のない花は　静かに眠るよ
Comment: 0,0:00:00.37,0:00:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.50,0:22:21.26,VIOLET_edch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}你的声音 指引我向前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.59,0:22:42.72,VIOLET_edch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}一只小鸟 婉转鸣叫着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.37,0:22:53.78,VIOLET_edch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}在未知的天空中 四处寻找我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.19,0:22:59.60,VIOLET_edch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}在温柔编织出的摇篮里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.86,0:23:05.24,VIOLET_edch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}向着明天前进
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.38,0:23:11.27,VIOLET_edch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}不论天晴 不论风雨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.59,0:23:15.96,VIOLET_edch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}只为能守护你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.44,0:23:26.87,VIOLET_edch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}独一无二的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.45,0:23:37.69,VIOLET_edch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}无名之花 静静地沉眠
